        <item>
            <title>日厂推全新卡式带录音机，免电脑卡式带转成 MP3、并可直接播带</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=kenko-tokina-kr019cr</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 16 Apr 2025 10:06:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[随身播放器]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kenko]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式带]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡式带转换]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1303628</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Kenko Tokina 即将推出「Kenko 便携式卡式带转换播放器 KR-019CR」，让用户可无需电脑轻松数码化卡式带，重温经典音色，配合 microSD 卡或 USB 记忆体即可转换成 MP3，内置扬声器亦可作卡式带播放器使用，支援语音录音及便携设计，适合怀旧音乐爱好者。</p><h2>无须电脑数码化卡式带</h2><p>Kenko 便携式卡式带转换播放器 KR-019CR 提供直观操作，无需连接电脑即可将卡式带转换为 MP3 格式，支援 microSDHC（4GB 至 32GB）、microSDXC（64GB 至 128GB）或 USB 记忆体（最高 128GB）。用户只需插入储存媒介，按下录制键，即可将旧日音色保存为数码档案，过程简单快捷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features01.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Kenko-Tokina</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 USB、micro SD，图片来源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2>可直接播放卡式带</h2><p>此播放器内置 76mm 扬声器，支援 3W 输出，可直接播放卡式带，无需额外连接任何装置。内置麦克风及 3.5mm 外置麦克风接口，方便录音。机身设有手柄，方便携带或悬挂，尺寸约 49 x 149 x 245mm，重量仅 685g，轻巧耐用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-694x578.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="578" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-694x578.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features04-scaled.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Kenko-Tokina</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features02.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身设有手柄，方便携带或悬挂，图片来源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2>灵活电源及兼容性</h2><p>KR-019CR 支援双电源模式，包括 AC 电源（DC5V/1.5A）及 4 颗 2 号碱性电池，电池续航力约 27 小时（音量 50% 时）。产品仅可使用普通卡式带，不支援高性能或金属卡式带。耳机输出为单声道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/kr019cr_features03.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Kenko-Tokina</p><h2></h2><h2>售价及开售详情</h2><p>KR-019CR 定价为 8,360 日元（约港币 456 元），将于 4 月 18 日发售。</p><p>订购连结：<a href="https://shop.kenko-tokina.co.jp/4961607446577">https://shop.kenko-tokina.co.jp/4961607446577</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/16/kenko-tokina-kr019cr/mobile-music/musicplayers/">日厂推全新卡式带录音机，免电脑卡式带转成 MP3、并可直接播带</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
